zohodesklink Plugin for DokuWiki

simply create links to zoho desk tickets

convert zd#1234 or zd#1234 direkt to https://<deskurl>/support/<deskname>/ShowHomePage.do#Cases/search/CurDep/1234

If you install this plugin manually, make sure it is installed in
lib/plugins/zohodesklink/ - if the folder is called different it
will not work!

Please refer to http://www.dokuwiki.org/plugins for additional info
on how to install plugins in DokuWiki.

